观看 Sabrina Carpenter 在 NPR 的 Tiny Desk 节目中首次亮相https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-她在 NPRS 小桌子上首次亮相Poppy BurtonSat, 21 Dec 2024 11:11:13 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3824246 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位“浓缩咖啡”歌手谈到了她作为“明显饥渴”流行歌星的名声</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246">观看 Sabrina Carpenter 在 NPR 的 Tiny Desk 上首次亮相的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨天（12 月 20 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>在 NPR 的<em>Tiny Desk</em>系列节目中首次亮相 - 请观看下面的表演片段。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/espresso-sabrina-carpenter-spotify-streaming-3757741"><b>为什么 Sabrina Carpenter 的“Espresso”会接管 Spotify 算法？</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>她在该系列节目中播放了她最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short &#39;n Sweet</a> 》中的曲目，其中包括关于露骨语言的警告，其中包括粉丝最喜欢的《Juno》和《Bad Chem》的演绎，并添加了新的小提琴安排。</p><p>在以《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-and-jenna-ortega-in-horror-inspired-taste-teaser-3785996">品味</a>》开场后，这位格莱美提名者回顾了她职业生涯的开始。 “当我第一次开始时，就是在这样的房间里，”她告诉观众。 “墙壁非常干燥，也没有像录音室里戴耳机时那样的混响，但它却非常真实。太特别了。”</p><p>在整个节目中，卡彭特分享了某些歌曲的诞生故事，以及她如何因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carptenter-scraps-custom-nonsense-outros-but-promises-surprise-cover-each-night-starting-with-abba-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-3796700">现已退休的“胡言乱语”结尾</a>而成为一名“明显饥渴”的流行歌星。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="萨布丽娜·卡彭特：小桌子音乐会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BEoGvTlJMyY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她将经常带有暗示的沉重尾声称为“美丽、快乐的意外”，并表示这些尾声激发了她下一张专辑的灵感，并在她开始创作“Short n&#39; Sweet”时给了她“无限的感觉”。</p><p>在表演的其他地方，她分享了“Bed Chem”的起源故事，这个故事是在与她最好的朋友帕洛玛同床共枕后发生的。当他们睡着并无意中同时醒来时，她打趣说他们有“非常好的床上用品”。</p><p> “所以我把它保存为标题，”她补充道。然后我遇到了一个人，我们有非常好的床上用品……她并没有靠它赚钱，所以我给了她很大的信任。” </p><figure id="attachment_3801038" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801038" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3801038" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 在麦迪逊广场花园举办的 Short N&#39; Sweet 巡演期间登台表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3801038" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 在麦迪逊广场花园举行的“Short N&#39; Sweet”巡演中登台表演。图片来源：克里斯托弗·波尔克（Christopher Polk）来自盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>《Bed Chem》最近被评为<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024"><em>NME</em> 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲</a>之一。瑞安·戴利 (Rhian Daly) 写道：“萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 将拥有自己的性取向变成了一种艺术，以至于她不得不否认自己是“世界上最性感的女孩”。</p><p> “床化学”并没有帮助解决问题。充满了厚颜无耻的歌词（“来吧，我的意思是友情”）和眨眼的委婉语，这首歌应该像《Espresso》一样无处不在。”</p><p> Carpenter 将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">明年将“Short N&#39; Sweet”巡演带到英国</a>，日期包括明年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535">在 BST 海德公园举行的大型头条节目</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsabrina-carpenter-tickets%2Fartist%2F2001092" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取门票</a>。</p><p> 2025 年，她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/CHAPPELL-ROAN">Chappell Roan</a>一起在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/primavera-sound-festival">Primavera Sound 上</a>亮相，并开始她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-uk-and-european-tour-for-2025-buy-tickets-3776153">英国和欧洲巡演</a>，巡演将于明年举行，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/rachel-chinouriri-15-01-2024-3570580"><em>NME</em>封面</a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a>将作为特邀嘉宾。</p><p>这些演出将于 3 月 3 日在都柏林 3Arena 拉开帷幕，随后还将在伯明翰、伦敦和曼彻斯特举办更多演出 - 请参阅下面的所有日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wr6WK%3A2K9xyKR7zUPb3vE3Q-UkCUhdxsCzkYRk0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>抢票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-make-her-debut-on-nprs-tiny-desk-3824246">观看 Sabrina Carpenter 在 NPR 的 Tiny Desk 上首次亮相的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
